  "notes": [
    "This case report describes a complex genetic evaluation involving mosaic TP53 variant requiring multiple confirmatory tests including tumor analysis and embryo testing",
    "The patient's management was significantly altered by the genetic findings, leading to bilateral mastectomy instead of breast-conserving surgery and avoidance of radiation therapy",
    "The case highlights the importance of distinguishing between germline, mosaic, and clonal hematopoiesis origins of TP53 variants for appropriate clinical management"
  ]
